  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Boutique Chain showcase: OBLONG with heavy filter (low cutoff, higher resonance) through Anomaly as the dominant effect. Anomaly TextureBlend 0.78 (maximum alternate texture) gives OBLONG a dense secondary timbral layer that adds mass to an already bass-heavy engine. ReverbSize 0.55. TremoloRate 0.8 Hz (slow but audible pulse). TimeSlip off — the weight should be stable. Archive Chance 0.05. Cathedral minimal DarkMix 0.45 — the Cathedral is present but not dominant. Submersion 4 stages at 0.12 Hz. The result is OBLONG as a heavy architectural element with Anomaly-derived depth and density.",
